<div data-fp-lazy-load-image></div>							</div>
			
			
<section class="bio-no-photo">
	<div>
		<p><strong>Saeed Jalili</strong> is a Tehran-based independent journalist. He has written for a variety of Iranian and international publications.&nbsp;Twitter:&nbsp;<a href="http://www.twitter.com/sjalilis" target="_blank">@sjalilis</a></p>	</div>
	<div class="last-author">
		<p><strong>Forough Alaei</strong> is a photojournalist based in Tehran, Iran. She's participated in VII Mentor Program since 2019.&nbsp;Twitter:&nbsp;<a href="http://www.twitter.com/foroughalaei" target="_blank">@foroughalaei</a>&nbsp;Instagram:&nbsp;<a href="http://instagram.com/foroughalaei" target="_blank">@foroughalaei</a></p>	</div>
